Here are all the relevant findings:

---

## 1. RPC Endpoints: `rpc.users.list` and `rpc.client.list`

### `rpc.users.list` — defined in `/home/aditya/projects/alpauls-ats/src/rpc/router/users.ts`

Registered as `users.list` in the router at `/home/aditya/projects/alpauls-ats/src/rpc/router/index.ts` (line 79):

```ts
users: {
  list: usersList,
},
```

The procedure accepts:
```ts
const listUsersSchema = z.object({
  cursor: z.string().optional(),
  includeBanned: z.boolean().optional(),
  limit: z.number().int().min(1).max(100).optional(),
  role: z.array(z.string()).optional(),  // filter by role(s)
  search: z.string().optional(),
});
```

It requires `permission: { action: "read", resource: "team_members" }` and returns `{ items, nextCursor }`. Each item has: `id`, `name`, `email`, `role`, `phoneNumber`, `image`, `banned`, `supervisorId`, `supervisorName`.

### `rpc.client.list` — defined in `/home/aditya/projects/alpauls-ats/src/rpc/router/client.ts`

Registered as `client.list` in the router (line 45):
```ts
client: {
  list: clientList,
  // ... also: archive, create, getById, getUploadUrl, listEvents, update
},
```

The procedure accepts:
```ts
const listClientsSchema = z.object({
  archived: z.boolean().optional(),
  assigneeId: z.array(z.string()).optional(),
  cursor: z.string().optional(),
  limit: z.number().int().min(1).max(100).optional(),
  search: z.string().optional(),
  sortBy: z.enum(["name", "createdAt"]).optional(),
  sortOrder: z.enum(["asc", "desc"]).optional(),
});
```

It requires `permission: { action: "read", resource: "clients" }` and returns `{ items, nextCursor }`.

**Key difference from `admin.listUsers`**: `rpc.users.list` is a public (filtered) listing, while `rpc.admin.listUsers` requires `manage-roles` permission on `team_members` and returns all users with full details (including `banExpires`, `banReason`, `createdAt`, `permissions`) — no cursor-based pagination, just a flat array.

---

## 2. What `#/forms` Exports — `/home/aditya/projects/alpauls-ats/integrations/forms/`

**Index file** (`/home/aditya/projects/alpauls-ats/integrations/forms/index.ts`):
```ts
